DESCRIPTION:
The Soviet Union invaded in Europe! Grabbing one country after another Soviet army turned west into a springboard for a new confrontation. Military operations are transferred to the United States. The West Coast of America destroyed, and U.S. forces continue to bear huge losses. Fierce fighting reached the middle of the continent, and no one believes in the victory over the Soviet Union. But the young commander defies the generals desperate! He will unite the scattered forces and carry out a big offensive. Lethal weapons and the latest technology in the face of the greatest battle!
